{"tid":83301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［求開解］畏懼死亡","createTime":"2017-01-16T15:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T03:41:07.000Z","uid":17242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"851c13e86055a35c5ae388c1f98734233f60624a","tid":83301,"uid":17242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"有時諗到自己終有一日會死就會覺得好驚<br />\n好恐懼 恐懼到有得種抖唔到氣既感覺<br />\n每次都係訓教前諗 搞到訓唔到<br />\n亦係到諗生存有咩意義<br />\n到底生存係為咗乜<br />\n當諗起生命迎接終結既一刻就會覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再出現咁可怕既感覺<br />\n<br />\n利申：毫無自殺傾向"},{"pid":"f1926915f7d928a7185f5ed188b0cf587caffbf7","tid":83301,"uid":17242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時諗到自己終有一日會死就會覺得好驚<br />\n好恐懼 恐懼到有種抖唔到氣既感覺<br />\n每次都係訓教前諗 搞到訓唔到<br />\n亦係到諗生存有咩意義<br />\n到底生存係為咗乜<br />\n當諗起生命迎接終結既一刻就會覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再出現咁可怕既感覺<br />\n<br />\n利申：毫無自殺傾向</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e23553513999f9e12dc7a0aaf05ac346eeebc347","tid":83301,"uid":65578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9864cfa3f44f5a2964093765d21b378c120b7ba","tid":83301,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"珍惜光陰<br />\n勿上連登"},{"pid":"c2efb5e98c515f0b8915977e9bb795093a150d89","tid":83301,"uid":17242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難受 好辛苦"},{"pid":"650f3e3841d94ac2825518f75dd2c459e6a948f4","tid":83301,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"生來就係要不斷發掘自己內在既潛能，繼而就係靈活運用。發掘得越多人生就越係成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千其唔好埋沒自己，多d去嘗試各樣嘢你先可以知邊飯係啱你"},{